        autocompletion functionality, this #[+Term--YDID function] may not&nbsp;be as convenient.
      Without autocompletion, you would need to memorize either #[+ImportantEntity__Code--YDID "mailto:"] or the
        #[+Term--YDID function] name #[+ImportantEntity__Code--YDID buildEmailLinkHrefAttributeValue].
      If you forget, which is common, you will need to refer to the documentation each time.


